La cosa sería unsink -¿sacar a flote?- lo que está hundido en ese "pantano"},
	annote = {autobiography is written not to provide a chronology of events related to the authors’ lives, with an account of the things they have done or that have happened to them, but rather to narrate the story of a self, of its trajectory through life, of the experiences that made the writers the human beings they are (...)
